rComments: Best professor at the university, make sure to take one of his classes!!

Prof. Newell is so clutch it's not even funny. The guy is just a professor from heaven, he's that awesome. He's down to earth and is really personable with students- you get the feeling that you're not just 1 of another 30,000 students when you're around him.

I had him for one of the easiest classes you can take beucase the book holds your hand through the course, didnt go to many lectures but he seemed like a very nice guy. If anyone asked a question he would help them out and not have an attitude at all. Great guy.
Awesome professor.  He is a brilliant man, and will help you out as much as u need.  If you can take atleast one class with him in your undergrad or grad career at UIUC.
He is great, he makes classes fun.  He understands how to teach classes to make them more effective and useful.  Uses a lot of group work and project work.  Great professor!
